    {
        "title" : "Angular Enterprise Dashboard - Phase 3B.4: Optimistic Updates — Local Mutations Without Re-Fetching",
        "date_published" : "2026-03-01T10:24:00+02:00",
        "date_modified" : "2026-03-01T10:53:36+02:00",
        "id" : "https://buffos.github.io/2026-03-18-phase-03b-part-04/",
        "url" : "https://buffos.github.io/2026-03-18-phase-03b-part-04/",
        "summary": "We\u0026rsquo;ve explored how resource() handles loading, cancellation, and all six status states. But there\u0026rsquo;s one pattern left that separates a good app from a great one: optimistic updates.\n",
        "content_html" : "\u003cp\u003eWe\u0026rsquo;ve explored how \u003ccode\u003eresource()\u003c/code\u003e handles \u003ca href=\"/2026-03-18-phase-03b-part-01\" rel=\"\"\u003eloading\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"/2026-03-18-phase-03b-part-02\" rel=\"\"\u003ecancellation\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"/2026-03-18-phase-03b-part-03\" rel=\"\"\u003eall six status states\u003c/a\u003e. But there\u0026rsquo;s one pattern left that separates a good app from a great one: \u003cstrong\u003eoptimistic updates\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch1 id=\"making-the-ui-respond-instantly\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#making-the-ui-respond-instantly\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eMaking the UI Respond Instantly\u003c/h1\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen a user clicks \u0026ldquo;Mark Complete\u0026rdquo; on a project, they don\u0026rsquo;t want to wait 400ms for a server round-trip to see the change. They want it \u003cem\u003enow\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"-the-concept-optimistic-ui\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#-the-concept-optimistic-ui\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e1 🧠 The Concept: Optimistic UI\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eAn optimistic update modifies the local data immediately — before the server confirms it. The UI reacts instantly, and the server sync happens in the background.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cpre class=\"mermaid\"\u003egraph LR\r\n    subgraph \"Traditional (Pessimistic)\"\r\n        Click1[\"User clicks 'Complete'\"] --\u003e Server1[\"Wait for Server\"]\r\n        Server1 --\u003e Update1[\"UI Updates\"]\r\n    end\r\n\r\n    subgraph \"Optimistic\"\r\n        Click2[\"User clicks 'Complete'\"] --\u003e LocalUpdate[\"UI Updates INSTANTLY\"]\r\n        LocalUpdate --\u003e ServerSync[\"Server sync (background)\"]\r\n    end\r\n\u003c/pre\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe trade-off: if the server rejects the change, you need to roll back. But for many operations (toggling status, incrementing counts, marking items), the success rate is so high that optimistic updates dramatically improve perceived speed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"-implementation-update\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#-implementation-update\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e2 🛠️ Implementation: \u003ccode\u003e.update()\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur \u003ccode\u003eProjectsComponent\u003c/code\u003e has a \u0026ldquo;Mark Complete\u0026rdquo; button on each card. Here\u0026rsquo;s the handler:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\r\n    \r\n    tw-flex \r\n    tw-flex-row\r\n    tw-flex-1 \r\n    tw-justify-between \r\n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\r\n    \"\u003e      \r\n    \u003cbutton \r\n      class=\"\r\n        code-block-button\r\n        tw-mx-2 \r\n        tw-flex\r\n        tw-flex-row\r\n        tw-flex-1\"\r\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003etypescript\u003c/p\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          line-number-button\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8h22.83a157.41 157.41 0 0 0-11 12.31l-5.61 7c-4 5.07-5.25 10.13-2.8 14.88l1.05 1.93c3 5.76 6.29 7.88 12.25 7.88h4.73c10.33 0 15.94 2.44 15.94 9.09 0 4.72-4.2 8.22-14.36 8.22a41.54 41.54 0 0 1-15.47-3.12c-6.49-3.88-11.74-3.5-15.6 3.12l-5.59 9.31c-3.72 6.13-3.19 11.72 2.63 15.94 7.71 4.69 20.38 9.44 37 9.44 34.16 0 48.5-22.75 48.5-44.12-.03-14.38-9.12-29.76-28.73-34.88zM496 224H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0-160H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V80a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0 320H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zM16 160h64a8 8 0 0 0 8-8v-16a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H64V40a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H32a8 8 0 0 0-7.14 4.42l-8 16A8 8 0 0 0 24 64h8v64H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8zm-3.91 160H80a8 8 0 0 0 8-8v-16a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H41.32c3.29-10.29 48.34-18.68 48.34-56.44 0-29.06-25-39.56-44.47-39.56-21.36 0-33.8 10-40.46 18.75-4.37 5.59-3 10.84 2.8 15.37l8.58 6.88c5.61 4.56 11 2.47 16.12-2.44a13.44 13.44 0 0 1 9.46-3.84c3.33 0 9.28 1.56 9.28 8.75C51 248.19 0 257.31 0 304.59v4C0 316 5.08 320 12.09 320z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          wrap-code-button\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle code wrap\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16 132h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16V76c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16C7.163 60 0 67.163 0 76v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16zm0 160h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16v-40c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16zm0 160h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16v-40c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n      \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          copy-code-button\r\n          tw-select-none\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden\r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block\r\n          hover:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\"\r\n        title=\"Copy code\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"copy-icon tw-block\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M433.941 65.941l-51.882-51.882A48 48 0 0 0 348.118 0H176c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v48H48c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v320c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h224c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48v-48h80c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V99.882a48 48 0 0 0-14.059-33.941zM266 464H54a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V150a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h74v224c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h96v42a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm128-96H182a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V54a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h106v88c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h88v202a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm6-256h-64V48h9.632c1.591 0 3.117.632 4.243 1.757l48.368 48.368a6 6 0 0 1 1.757 4.243V112z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"check-icon tw-hidden\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n        \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-hidden \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        disabled\r\n        aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \r\n    id=\"codeblock-id-9\" \r\n    class=\"\r\n      chroma \r\n      !tw-block \r\n      tw-p-0\r\n      tw-m-0\r\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \r\n      tw-duration-500 \r\n      tw-ease-in-out \r\n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \r\n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\r\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\r\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\r\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\r\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003emarkComplete\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eproject\u003c/span\u003e: \u003cspan class=\"kt\"\u003eProject\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003evoid\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ethis\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eprojectsResource\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eupdate\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ecurrent\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e    \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003eif\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e!\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ecurrent\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ereturn\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ecurrent\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e    \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ereturn\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ecurrent\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003emap\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ep\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e      \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ep\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eid\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e===\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eproject\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eid\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e        \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e?\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e...\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ep\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003estatus\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;completed\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kr\"\u003eas\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kr\"\u003econst\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eprogress\u003c/span\u003e: \u003cspan class=\"kt\"\u003e100\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e        \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ep\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e    \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e});\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003ch3 id=\"whats-happening\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#whats-happening\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e2.1 What\u0026rsquo;s Happening\u003c/h3\u003e\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.update()\u003c/code\u003e receives the current resource value (the project array).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe return a \u003cstrong\u003enew array\u003c/strong\u003e with the target project\u0026rsquo;s status changed to \u003ccode\u003e'completed'\u003c/code\u003e and progress set to \u003ccode\u003e100\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe resource\u0026rsquo;s \u003ccode\u003evalue()\u003c/code\u003e signal updates immediately.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe resource\u0026rsquo;s \u003ccode\u003estatus()\u003c/code\u003e transitions to \u003ccode\u003e'local'\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNo server request is made.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"-the-local-status\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#-the-local-status\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e3 🟡 The \u003ccode\u003e'local'\u003c/code\u003e Status\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter an \u003ccode\u003e.update()\u003c/code\u003e call, the resource enters the \u003ccode\u003e'local'\u003c/code\u003e status. This is Angular\u0026rsquo;s way of saying: \u003cem\u003e\u0026ldquo;The data you\u0026rsquo;re seeing has been modified locally and may not match the server.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe show a visual notice to make this transparent:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\r\n    \r\n    tw-flex \r\n    tw-flex-row\r\n    tw-flex-1 \r\n    tw-justify-between \r\n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\r\n    \"\u003e      \r\n    \u003cbutton \r\n      class=\"\r\n        code-block-button\r\n        tw-mx-2 \r\n        tw-flex\r\n        tw-flex-row\r\n        tw-flex-1\"\r\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003ehtml\u003c/p\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          line-number-button\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8h22.83a157.41 157.41 0 0 0-11 12.31l-5.61 7c-4 5.07-5.25 10.13-2.8 14.88l1.05 1.93c3 5.76 6.29 7.88 12.25 7.8